description:
1️⃣ A sword that feels uncomfortably weighty towards the
blade. Still swingable, and would still cut shit.
name: Imbalanced Sword

description:
2️⃣ Impeccably normal and regularly-forged iron sword.
Is kinda heavy, though.
name: Iron Blade

description:
3️⃣ A massive blade that simply cannot be wielded in one-hand.
Though you can't wield an offhand, this weapon is immensely powerful.
name: Two-Handed Sword

description:
⭐ A sword whose blade is a perfect 90 degree angle from it's cross-guard.
It is a bit rough around the edges, but serious potential is there.
name: "Straight Edge"

description:
4️⃣ A classic sword that shows up in every game.
This one is made of an aluminum-like alloy, making it light and easy to wield.
name: Scimitar

description:
5️⃣ A superbly forged blade of noire.
Attacks are also void-elemental and may inflict \State[23](20%).
name: Night Slash

description:

Takes two hands to wield.

description:

description:
⭐ It might be... from a foreign land... but it also might be a knock-off... At least it looks flashy?
Takes two hands to wield.

description:
1️⃣ An aging revolver that can still shoot bullets (somehow...).
Takes a lot of effort to get it working consistently, though.
name: Old Revolver

description:
2️⃣ Why would you silence a revolver? Who knows, but you do run
a bit faster and feel a bit nimbler when wielding this gun.
name: Silenced Revolver

description:
3️⃣ This looks like a pistol, but it is literally a cannon that
fires a shrapnel-like bullet that really packs a "bang".
name: Bang Blaster

description:
⭐ There is no way this gun cannot result in bloodshed when fired.
Each shot can hit twice.
name: "Bloody Mary"

description:
4️⃣ The standard in modern-day pistol weapons.
Fires regular bullets that deal regular damage.

description:
1️⃣ A hatchet that is fairly rusty. Maybe would poison your
enemies as well as hurt them?
name: Rusty Hatchet

description:
2️⃣ A uniquely green axe bearing the poison from an elder wolftrap.
The poison is deadly, considering the axe otherwise is not.
name: Wolftrap Axe

description:
3️⃣ A huge axe that simply couldn't be wielded in one hand.
But smashing foes just got easier since two-hand axe means faster slashing!
name: Knight's Axe

description:
⭐ A farmer's decree that ALL wheat MUST FALL.
Also can be used to lop off enemies' heads like you would with an axe.
name: "Farmer's Decree"

description:
4️⃣ The unique shape of the blade makes this a favorite of goblins.
Swing it with big sweeping slashes, make sure you mop up your foes with their blood!
name: Curled Axe

Can be used to bonk people on their heads, but probably shouldn't be.
name: Aged Staff

description: 2️⃣ A cute little kappa-themed wand, imbued with the liquid element.
name: Kappa Wand

description:
3️⃣ Its tough to discern where this originally came from, but wherever
it was, it must've been magical.

description:
⭐ It is hard to believe this is even a little magical, but it is glowing.
Bestows the "Rapid Cinders I" skill.
name: "Magic Torch"

description:
1️⃣ A glove that has seen many an action.
What that action was remains a mystery, so just wear it.
name: Worn Glove

description:
2️⃣ You only punch with one hand, so it is easiest to put both gloves on
the same hand for double the power!
name: Leather Fists

description:
3️⃣ It is said that the metal plate protecting the knuckles is actually
your butler's essence, protecting you even beyond transmutation punishment.
name: Royal Slappers

description:
⭐ With these, now you punch with the added force of 1000 angry rocks!
A bit heavier than lower-tier gloves.
name: "IRON FIST"
